---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Academic Markdown Template">
  <section class="card">
    <h1>Academic Markdown Template</h1>
    <p>
      Copy the file at <strong>src/content/academic/_template.md</strong>, rename it with a new slug,
      then fill the fields. It will appear automatically in Academic list and detail pages.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>图片双模式：</strong>支持本地路径（/images/...、./、../）和远程 URL（https://...）。</li>
      <li><strong>严格容错：</strong>缺失或格式错误的 rating/link/images 会在页面显示 warning。</li>
      <li><strong>推荐写法：</strong>本地图片统一放到 <strong>public/images</strong> 并使用 <strong>/images/...</strong>。</li>
    </ul>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--line);
    border-radius: 16px;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(16, 37, 61, 0.05);
    padding: 1.2rem;
  }

  h1 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  p {
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  ul {
    margin: 0.8rem 0 0;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.75;
  }
</style>
